{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"class","modules":[{"name":"SwiftGodot"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ReflectionProbe","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"ReflectionProbe","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"ReflectionProbe","externalID":"s:10SwiftGodot15ReflectionProbeC","roleHeading":"Class"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Captures its surroundings to create fast, accurate reflections from a given point."}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/ambientColor","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/ambientColorEnergy","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/ambientMode-swift.property","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/boxProjection","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/cullMask","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/enableShadows","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/intensity","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/interior","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/maxDistance","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/meshLodThreshold","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/originOffset","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/size","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/updateMode-swift.property"]},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/godotClassName"],"title":"Type Properties"},{"title":"Enumerations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/AmbientMode-swift.enum","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/UpdateMode-swift.enum"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"ReflectionProbe","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Captures its surroundings as a cubemap, and stores versions of it with increasing levels of blur to simulate different material roughnesses."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe"},{"type":"text","text":" is used to create high-quality reflections at a low performance cost (when "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/updateMode-swift.property","isActive":true},{"text":" is .updateOnce). ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"s can be blended together and with the rest of the scene smoothly. ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe"},{"type":"text","text":"s can also be combined with "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/VoxelGI","type":"reference"},{"text":", SDFGI (","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Environment\/sdfgiEnabled","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":") and screen-space reflections ("},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Environment\/ssrEnabled"},{"text":") to get more accurate reflections in specific areas. ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"s render all objects within their "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe\/cullMask","isActive":true},{"text":", so updating them can be quite expensive. It is best to update them once with the important static objects and then leave them as-is.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Unlike ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/VoxelGI"},{"type":"text","text":" and SDFGI, "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"s only source their environment from a "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/WorldEnvironment"},{"text":" node. If you specify an ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Environment","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" resource within a "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Camera3D","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" node, it will be ignored by the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":". This can lead to incorrect lighting within the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Note","style":"note","type":"aside"},{"type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Reflection probes are only supported in the Forward+ and Mobile rendering methods, not Compatibility. When using the Mobile rendering method, only 8 reflection probes can be displayed on each mesh resource. Attempting to display more than 8 reflection probes on a single mesh resource will result in reflection probes flickering in and out as the camera moves."}]}],"name":"Note"},{"style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When using the Mobile rendering method, reflection probes will only correctly affect meshes whose visibility AABB intersects with the reflection probe’s AABB. If using a shader to deform the mesh in a way that makes it go outside its AABB, "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/GeometryInstance3D\/extraCullMargin"},{"text":" must be increased on the mesh. Otherwise, the reflection probe may not be visible on the mesh.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Note"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/reflectionprobe"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ReflectionProbe","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"inheritsFrom","kind":"relationships","title":"Inherits From","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/VisualInstance3D"]},{"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/GodotObject","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/s23CustomStringConvertibleP","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/SQ","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/SH","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/s12IdentifiableP","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/VariantRepresentable","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/VariantStorable"]}],"references":{"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot/ReflectionProbe/godotClassName":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"godotClassName","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeI